Title: 10 hurt as rival TDP groups clash
Content: Dispute over a contract work under the government’s Neeru-Chettu scheme led to a clash between rival Telugu Desam Party workers in Kadapa district on Wednesday, resulting in injuries to 10 persons.Fol
Author: Special Correspondent
Description: Dispute over a contract work under the government’s Neeru-Chettu scheme led to a clash between rival Telugu Desam Party workers in Kadapa district on Wednesday, resulting in injuries to 10 persons.Fol
